    "• Temperature dependence of heavy quark masses The heavy quark mass is independent of temperature.",
    "• Equilibrium limits in transport We use the Boltzmann equation to describe the dissociation and regeneration of quarkonium in relativistic heavy-ion collisions.",
    "The dissociation and regeneration are related to each other via the detailed balance.",
    "Thus, the equilibrium limit is naturally satisfied.• Constraints from lattice QCD The in-medium heavyquark potential is close to the internal energy extracted from the lattice QCD calculations.",
